      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for reliable transportation. The exterior shows its age with various surface scratches, some minor paint fading on the hood, and a few small dings around the door panels. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows noticeable wear and a few faint stains from regular use. While it runs and drives well, the engine bay could use a cleaning and it will eventually need new tires. It is a solid choice for someone who prioritizes functionality over aesthetics.",
