    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering. Under the hood, the S54 straight-six screams to an 8,000 RPM redline, featuring a meticulously maintained double-VANOS system and recently replaced rod bearings for total peace of mind. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via the factory M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis is flawless, featuring documented subframe reinforcement and a suspension setup that retains its original factory-spec damping and lateral stiffness. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the paint retains its deep luster with zero oxidation, while the undercarriage is dry and free of any electrolytic corrosion. This is a collector-grade example with a linear power band and surgical steering rack precision.",
