      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom-fresh condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since its original purchase. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather seats show no signs of creasing or bolster wear, and the original protective films remain on several interior trim pieces. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has followed a rigorous maintenance schedule exclusively at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive binder of service records included. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions exactly as intended. The engine bay is pristine, reflecting the obsessive care this vehicle has received. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a turn-key masterpiece that looks, smells, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Includes two sets of keys, the original window sticker, and a clean, accident-free history.",
